# CODEOWNERS for the auditor-suite hub.
#
# This file routes pull-request review automatically. The current maintainer
# is @hannsxpeter; the default rule covers everything. Path-specific rules
# below make the high-blast-radius surfaces explicit, so a future
# co-maintainer can see at a glance which files trigger which reviewers.

# Default fallback: hub maintainer reviews everything.
* @hannsxpeter

# SUITE.md is the suite map every consumer reads. Changes cascade to docs.
/SUITE.md @hannsxpeter

# Install/uninstall scripts touch every consumer's filesystem. Bash 3.2
# regressions and harness-detection mistakes break user installs silently.
/install.sh @hannsxpeter
/uninstall.sh @hannsxpeter

# The meta-linter mechanically enforces suite discipline. A check that fails
# to fail silently degrades the protection the suite has against drift.
/scripts/ @hannsxpeter

# CI workflows. A workflow regression cascades to every push.
/.github/workflows/ @hannsxpeter

# Plugin marketplace manifest. A manifest typo breaks Claude Code's
# /plugin install command for every consumer.
/.claude-plugin/marketplace.json @hannsxpeter
